stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Constructed
    Constructed --> Running: start worker thread
    Running --> Queued: callback(topic, msg)
    Queued --> Running: worker drains request
    Running --> Closing: close()
    Closing --> ShutdownQueued: enqueue shutdown request
    ShutdownQueued --> Joined: worker exits and join returns
    Joined --> DelegateClosed: wrapped agent.close()
    DelegateClosed --> [*]

    note right of Running
      One worker thread serializes callbacks
      for the wrapped concrete agent.
    end note
